        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Respect for Peace Corps Volunteers Act </strong></p> <p>This bill allows the official seal or emblem of the Peace Corps and the name <i>Peace Corps</i> to be used on any death announcement, plaque, grave stone, or other grave marker of a former volunteer, officer, or employee of the Peace Corps.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
